<p>Dear <%= @advisee %>,</p>
<p>Congratulations on successful deposit of your <%= @work.degree %> thesis to Libra, the University of Virginia's scholarly repository.</p>
<p>The work you have deposited in Libra will be available for <%= @availability %>. You have opted to grant <%= @work.rights.join(' ') %> to users of your scholarship.</p>
<% if @is_sis_thesis %>
	24 hours after deposit, you may check that your scholarship was successfully added to the Library's collection by searching for your thesis or dissertation in VIRGO, the UVA online library catalog.
	48 hours after deposit, <a href="http://www.its.virginia.edu/sis/">please verify that SIS has been updated</a> to reflect that you have completed this requirement.
<% else %>
<p>Your completion of this requirement is being reported to your department by copy of this email. If you have any questions about your degree status, please contact your school of enrollment.</p>
<% end %>
<p>The permanent location for your scholarship is <a href="<%= @doi_link %>"><%= @doi_link %></a>.</p>
<p>Always provide this exact link when sharing your work with colleagues, collaborators, and on social media for the most accurate metrics on views and downloads.</p>
<% if !@is_sis_thesis %>
<p>24 hours after deposit, you may check that your scholarship was successfully added to the Library's collection by searching for your thesis or dissertation in VIRGO, the UVA online library catalog.</p>
<% end %>
<p></p>
<p>Best Regards,</p>
<p>Scholarly Repository Services, University of Virginia Library</p>
<p>libra@virginia.edu</p>
